<div class="fcs-simple-text">
    <div class="fcs-simple-text__body bg-site">
        <h2 class="fcs-simple-text__title">Teams</h2>
        <div class="fcs-simple-text__copy"><p>From speaking to customers each day to building the trading platforms of tomorrow, our teams help people build their financial futures.</p></div>
