            <div class="fcs-slider__body">
                <div class="fcs-slider__intro">
                    <div class="fcs-simple-text">
                        <div class="fcs-simple-text__body bg-site">
                            <h2 class="fcs-simple-text__title">Benefits that build around your life</h2>
                            <div class="fcs-simple-text__copy"><p>Our programs are designed to empower our associates to live their best lives at work and at home.</p></div>
